correctness.rationale: Major factual and schema issues. (1) Incomplete processes: Article reports three ALD infiltrations (TiO2: 90 cycles; ZnO: 80 cycles; Al2O3: 100 cycles), but only one ZnO process is extracted. (2) Wrong dosing/purge times: Article states 1 s exposures and 20 s purges; extracted uses 1 and 20 with unit MilliSEC (ms), i.e., 1 ms and 20 ms. To comply with the schema’s MilliSEC unit, values should be 1000 ms and 20000 ms. (3) Incorrect GPC: For ZnO, article gives 0.2 nm/cycle; extracted gives 0.2 Å/cycle (10× too small). Should be 2 Å or 0.2 nm. (4) Schema violation: processParameters.plasmaPower is set to None, but the schema defines it as an object; omit if not used. (5) Numerous untraceable/fabricated values: flowRates (10 SCM-PER-MIN), saturation=True, nucleationPeriod=1 cycle, filmThickness=16 nm, material properties (absorptionCoefficient=0, bandGap=3.3 eV, electrical properties, uniformity, conformality, composition, crystallinity=XRD, roughness=AFM, density=XRR), and all deviceProperties—none are reported in the paper. (6) Some correct items: TALD, precursors (DEtZn/H2O), N2 carrier/purge, temperature 85 °C, pressure ~10 Torr (mmHg), substrate glass, and refractive index n≈2.0 for ZnO. Overall, the extraction is largely ungrounded and contains key numerical/unit errors and missing processes.

completeness.rationale: Major incompleteness and factual misalignment. (1) Multiple processes missing: the article reports three ALD infiltrations (TiO2: TiCl4/H2O, 90 cycles; ZnO: DEtZn/H2O, 80 cycles; Al2O3: TMA/H2O, 100 cycles) under the same conditions (85 °C, ~10 Torr, N2). The extraction includes only ZnO. Separate process objects for TiO2 and Al2O3 are required with their specific precursors, cycles, and GPCs (0.17, 0.2, 0.15 nm/cycle, respectively). (2) Unit errors/inconsistencies: dosing and purge times are 1 s and 20 s in the article but recorded as 1 and 20 MilliSEC (ms). If schema restricts to MilliSEC, values must be 1000 ms and 20000 ms. ZnO growth-per-cycle is given as 0.2 Å instead of 0.2 nm (should be 2 Å if using Å), creating inconsistency. (3) Numerous untraceable/fabricated values: flow rates (10 sccm), saturation=True, nucleationPeriod=1 cycle, supercycleDesign, most material properties (band gap, absorption, roughness, density, composition, crystallinity), electrical properties, and TFT device metrics are not reported in the article. (4) Partial correctness: temperature (85 °C), pressure (~10 Torr mmHg), carrier/purging gas (N2), substrate (glass), ZnO precursor/co-reactant are correct; film thickness 16 nm is consistent with 80 cycles × 0.2 nm but conflicts with the mis-stated GPC unit. To improve, add two additional ALD process objects (TiO2 and Al2O3) with correct precursor pairs, cycles, GPCs, and shared conditions; correct time and GPC units; remove or leave out properties not supported by the text; ensure all remaining values are traceable to the article.
